data.description: Seller will pay $30,000 towards buyers closing costs or towards a 3-2-1 buydown with preferred lender! This elegant and spacious 4-bedroom 3.5 bath home is located in the beautiful Mussett Bayou Manor community.  Step into the foyer and take in the 10-foot ceilings and tons of natural light.  The open layout features a gourmet kitchen with GE Profile appliances including a gas countertop range, stainless vent hood, and double wall ovens. There is ample cabinetry storage and a walk-in pantry. The huge island seats six and is perfect for entertaining. A half bath is located on the first floor. All bedrooms and the laundry room are located on the second floor which boasts 9-ft ceilings.  The huge primary-suite offers coffered ceilings, 2 walk-in closets, an ensuite with double vanity, walk-in shower and a soaking tub.  Step out of the primary bedroom onto the second-floor balcony where yocan enjoy privacy at the end of your day.
